2020-05-25T03:01:35.000Z","msg":"落實有得走先鳩啦<br />\n<br />\n講到實比你走咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc6b75d166160134d7839a242f2502585aad3f8","tid":2033894,"uid":304769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:01:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">BNO平權正視聽</span></span><br />\n連登一向有大量風向L、放負L，睇到BNO平權消息就用<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>割97後等風向挑撥離間</strong></span>，大家上連登請帶埋個腦。<br />\n<br />\n我從六月開始打英國戰線，希望嚮呢度講幾句。<br />\n第一，BNO平權唔會割97後，因為我地一向都係爭取救<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">BNO及其後代</span></strong>。，除非你係雙非，否則幾乎一定會受惠。<br />\n第二，BNO平權絕對係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>同美國行動有關係</strong></span>，故此毫無疑問就係一個救手足之舉，甚至可能與<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">軍事撤僑</span></strong>有關。<br />\n第三，BNO平到權主要唔係用包機包船黎接香港人去英國，亦都冇咩可能會接，畢竟人數太多。平到權最大重點係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>BNO變正式英國國民，中共逼害英國國民嘅話，英國以至美國就有理由做野</strong></span>。<br />\n第四，BNO平權估計會<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">寬鬆處理，英屬香港人（BOTC、BDTC、CUKC）無BNO或者已經過期應該都ok</span></strong>。因為英國情報已經判斷香港情況差到似烏干達難民。<br />\n第五，BNO平權大家可以更加無後顧之憂，因為將來要良民證黎移民，可以向英國當局申請。"},{"pid":"e577d102d96e91e6842898b44f50fcd3c9118a59","tid":2033894,"uid":71341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:17:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c8da4dcd8f499fc8944cf57f9a291bc56a95cc9","tid":2033894,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:21:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>三毛勿覆</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"002217a96918a4d98afb50dccfd11121d8b104d7","tid":2033894,"uid":61057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:21:41.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"895c593996e07f6a8242764e206853de5019850c","tid":2033894,"uid":358640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"825f1fcf014cc2172846073443d415dc73dee9e6","tid":2033894,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05